{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","author_sig":"{\"payload\": \"\", \"payloadType\": \"application/vnd.rebar.authorship.v1+json\", \"signatures\": [{\"keyid\": \"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d\", \"sig\": \"\"}]}","data":{"fields":{"description":"## Description\nDocument the new surface so clients can adopt it. GROUNDED FACTS (verified against the dependency tickets, resolving the blocking finding):\n- A `[metrics]` pip EXTRA IS created by ticket 9597 and contains ONLY `lizard` (the complexity analyzer, imported as a library via `guard_import(extra=\"metrics\")`).\n- `scc` and `jscpd` are EXTERNAL CLI prerequisites (PATH binaries), NOT pip deps and NOT part of the extra. Document them as separate install prerequisites.\n- So adoption = `pip install rebar[metrics]` (lizard) PLUS installing scc + jscpd on PATH. Document all three precisely; do not imply scc/jscpd come via the extra.\n\n## Review-driven corrections\n- `tests/scripts/test_metrics_docs.py` ALREADY exists (ticket 121b) with a narrower contract — EXTEND it; existing assertions must still pass.\n- Config keys documented in `docs/config.md` (canonical config design-of-record) in addition to user-guide + reuse-surface.\n- Content prerequisite is 0734s FINAL shape (relates_to edge recorded).\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- [ ] docs/reuse-surface.md: analyzer seam + the `[metrics]` extra (lizard only) + scc/jscpd as separate PATH prerequisites.\n- [ ] docs/config.md: `[code_health]` keys/types/defaults; docs/user-guide.md Metrics section: the three-part install (extra + scc + jscpd) + \"no analyzer -> Unavailable\" behavior.\n- [ ] AGENTS.md metrics pointer updated if the one-liner changed.\n- [ ] tests/scripts/test_metrics_docs.py extended; existing assertions still pass.\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] test_metrics_docs.py passes (old + new assertions); docs lint clean.\n\n## Dependencies: 0734 (content prerequisite; relates_to edge recorded).\n## Files likely touched: docs/reuse-surface.md, docs/config.md, docs/user-guide.md, AGENTS.md, tests/scripts/test_metrics_docs.py\n## Estimated scope: M"}},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"EDIT","timestamp":1784530335162657001,"uuid":"5c98b6aa-e0c6-48af-9acf-640ffbc2fe79"}